column100:
We are looking for service-minded staff members to join our small team on Christianshavn!  
 We are looking for both experienced and un-experienced staff right now and look forward to welcoming you to a nice work environment, happy guests and a beautiful restaurant.  
 We don´t tolerate any form of racism, sexism or bad behavior and celebrate diversity and great team players.  
 We look forward to hearing from you!  
 Team Lola
